sub_title: Extending the enterprise IT lifecycle @Ynvolve B.V. ✔ Providing cost-effective IT Hardware solutions
summary:
Curious | Dynamic | Empathetic

Born and raised in France, I developed a deep fascination for culture due to my experiences that has seen me live in Germany, England, Mexico and most recently, the Netherlands. Through this I have built an ability to adapt to different cultures and experiences, as well as to challenge myself to further support my growth in business and as a person.

With a background in Business Administration, Marketing, and International Trade, I now focus on:

- Reinforcing and developing business relations with VAR’s, multi-national end users and webhosters
- Providing customized cost-effective hardware enterprise solutions (servers/storage/networking)

You are in the IT industry? Know that I am always open to expand my network and relationships so, if you feel we can create a mutually beneficial relationship, feel free to reach out by inMail or e-mail (p.naudin@ynvolve.com). Be sure I'll try my best to help you!
